[SIZE="3"][B]Steps:[/B][/SIZE]

Download Candy5.zip
Download 5.0.+ Gapps (optional)
Place Candy5.zip on phones memory or SD card
Boot into recovery (either twrp or cwm)
Full wipe (Dalvik Cache, Cache, System, Factory Data Reset)
Flash Candy5.zip 
Flash Gapps
Flash SuperSu zip (optional)
Reboot and Enjoi

[IMG]http://img.tapatalk.com/d/14/07/05/be9apenu.jpg[/IMG]

*[B][URL="]Candy5[/URL][/B]

* [B][URL="https://s.basketbuild.com/gapps"]Gapps[/URL][/B]
Or use 5.0.0 Gapps of choice

* [B][URL="http://forum.xda-developers.com/showthread.php?t=1538053"]SuperSU[/URL][/B]


[B][Color="RED"]Please give first boot a good few minutes.[/COLOR][/B]

Candy5 is in early stages and will inherit CyanogenMod bugs and issues. But some we have resolved ourselves.
The base has been tested and passed most users needs for a Daily Driver. 


